{
  "texts": [
    "It is important to study the effectiveness of the training strategy proposed in Sect. 5.2.",
    "Such a study will highlight the challenges, complexity and cost involved in training jointly all the variants.",
    "Such a study will also help us in understanding the accuracy and exit probabilities achieved at each exit branch.",
    "Early-exit decision making As discussed in Sect. 5.3, we evaluated our learningbased module for exit decision-making exclusively on one DNN variant with two exit branches, where 30.94% of requests exit at the first exit branch with a minimal drop in accuracy.",
    "It is important to study how well our learning-based module performs across all DNN variants."
  ]
}